fields.name: Basic Glazed Donut
fields.description: No frills. A little boring. But it's exactly what you need right now. Trust us.

fields.name: Lemon Filled Donut
fields.description: It's like eating a big, squishy lemon-flavored beetle that bursts open when you bite it.

fields.name: Chocolate Donut
fields.description: It has a lot of chocolate on it. But not too much. Exactly the right amount of chocolate.

fields.name: Chocolate Creme Filled Donut
fields.description: There's so much chocolate in here. Like, guys, why did we add so much chocolate.

fields.name: Chocolate Donut with Sprinkles
fields.description: Not only is it chocolate, but it is also sprinkles.

fields.name: Jelly Donut
fields.description: You will be overwhelmed by the jelly. That's our solemn promise to you.

fields.name: Strawberry Donut with Sprinkles
fields.description: As if strawberry wasn't good enough already.

fields.name: Maple Bacon Donut
fields.description: We think this one is pretty gross but y'all keep asking for it. You monsters.
